OL,3,C'I just wanted to explain': Alleged
OL,4,CMcCann stalker explains 'persistent'
OL,5,Ccalls
OL,7,FA woman accused of stalking Madeleine
OL,8,FMcCann's parents from Leicestershire,
OL,9,Fhas told a jury she persisted in
OL,10,Fcalling Kate McCann because she wanted
OL,11,Fto help her, but would "respect her
OL,12,Fdecision" if the mother told her to
OL,13,Fleave her alone.
OL,15,FJulia Wandelt told the jury at
OL,16,FLeicester Crown Court she did not mean
OL,17,Fto upset Mrs McCann, adding that she
OL,18,Fwanted to assist her.
