OL,3,C'I just wanted to explain': Alleged
OL,4,CMcCann stalker explains 'persistent'
OL,5,Ccalls
OL,7,FShe said: "I got the impression that
OL,8,Fpolice did not pass any information to
OL,9,FKate and Gerry. I just thought they
OL,10,Fwere misled and I just wanted to
OL,11,Fexplain."
OL,13,FWandelt said she wanted to speak to
OL,14,FMrs McCann to "explain all the pieces
OL,15,Fof evidence" and the memories she had,
OL,16,Fadding that the chance she could be
OL,17,FMadeleine outweighed the "potential
OL,18,Fdisappointment" for the McCanns.
