OL,3,C'I just wanted to explain': Alleged
OL,4,CMcCann stalker explains 'persistent'
OL,5,Ccalls
OL,7,FShe said: "If you compared false hope
OL,8,Fand potential truth coming out... I'm
OL,9,Fnot a mother but I have younger
OL,10,Fsiblings. If my sister or brother went
OL,11,Fmissing I would do everything... if I
OL,12,Fhad a little hope."
OL,14,FProsecutors allege Wandelt peddled the
OL,15,Fmyth she was Madeleine, who went
OL,16,Fmissing aged three during a family
OL,17,Fholiday in Portugal in 2007, while
OL,18,Fstalking Kate and Gerry McCann by
OL,19,Fsending emails, making phone calls and
OL,20,Fturning up at their address in Rothley
OL,21,Fin Leicestershire.
