OL,3,C'I just wanted to explain': Alleged
OL,4,CMcCann stalker explains 'persistent'
OL,5,Ccalls
OL,7,FThe court previously heard that
OL,8,FWandelt called and messaged Mrs McCann
OL,9,Fmore than 60 times in one day in April
OL,10,Flast year.
OL,12,F"I thought that DNA should be done"
OL,14,FDefence barrister Tom Price KC asked
OL,15,FWandelt why she "persisted" in trying
OL,16,Fto contact Mrs McCann after receiving
OL,17,Fno response.
OL,26,@tD@AOUwD@QOUwD@[O]
