OL,3,C'I just wanted to explain': Alleged
OL,4,CMcCann stalker explains 'persistent'
OL,5,Ccalls
OL,7,FWandelt told the court: "I thought
OL,8,Fthat DNA should be done, it should
OL,9,Fhave been done in the beginning and I
OL,10,Fdidn't understand.
OL,12,F"I thought it was because of the
OL,13,Fmedia, because of what they said about
OL,14,Fme. I thought maybe that was the
OL,15,Freason why she didn't want to do the
OL,16,FDNA test, because maybe she was told
OL,17,FI'm crazy or that I am lying."
OL,19,FMr Price asked: "Did you think if you
OL,20,Fhad a chance to speak to her, you
OL,21,Fcould persuade her you weren't crazy?"
OL,26,@oD@YOUtD@AOUyD@^O]{D@QOU}D@fO]
