OL,3,C'I just wanted to explain': Alleged
OL,4,CMcCann stalker explains 'persistent'
OL,5,Ccalls
OL,7,FWandelt replied: "Yes. There was no
OL,8,Fengagement from her, nothing, and
OL,9,Fthere was something odd about it. It
OL,10,Fwas all the time silence, I just
OL,11,Fdidn't understand."
OL,13,FAsked what would have made her stop
OL,14,Fthe phone calls, Wandelt said: "A
OL,15,Fconversation with me and a DNA test."
