OL,3,C'I just wanted to explain': Alleged
OL,4,CMcCann stalker explains 'persistent'
OL,5,Ccalls
OL,7,FMr Price asked what she would do if
OL,8,FMrs McCann asked her to leave her
OL,9,Falone, and Wandelt said: "If she
OL,10,Fcalled me, after listening to my
OL,11,Fevidence and giving me the chance to
OL,12,Fexplain... I think I would respect
OL,13,Fthis."
OL,15,FWandelt and her co-defendant, Karen
OL,16,FSpragg, 61, of Caerau Court Road in
OL,17,FCaerau, Cardiff, both deny one count
OL,18,Fof stalking between June 2022 and
OL,19,FFebruary this year.
OL,21,FThe trial continues.
